      • setRunningActivitySupplier

        public static void setRunningActivitySupplier(ActivityUtils.Supplier<android.app.Activity> activitySupplier)
        Sets the Supplier for the running (a.k.a. resumed or foreground) activity. Called from TestRunner. If a custom runner is used, this method must be called appropriately, otherwise getRunningActivity() won't work.

      • getRunningActivity

        public static android.app.Activity getRunningActivity()
        Gets the running (a.k.a. resumed or foreground) activity. InstrumentationDriver depends on this.
        Returns:
        the currently running activity, or null if no activity has focus.
